CoinGecko $UWON
This meme-coin is dedicated to the launch of Case Boom game in Telegram Wallet. At the end of the game there was a funny bug when instead of a box there was an empty screen and the title YOU WON.
Tens of thousands of people saw this screen and we decided to launch a meme-coin dedicated to it. Let's send UWON to the moon to prove that we really won 😉
